<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='750630' id='t-750630'>with a generic approach,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='752724' id='t-752724'>and it's not just the slides,
it's what they mean.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='755447' id='t-755447'>And it's how they link together.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='757072' id='t-757072'>And so I'm going to be conducting
