<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='765542' id='t-765542'>to come and then give it en masse,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='767795' id='t-767795'>in communities all across the country,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='770000' id='t-770000'>and we're going to update the slideshow
