to be a Democrat.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='803935' id='t-803935'>We need Republicans as well.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='805464' id='t-805464'>This used to be a bipartisan issue,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='807497' id='t-807497'>and I know that
in this group it really is.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='809978' id='t-809978'>Become politically active.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='811554' id='t-811554'>Make our democracy work the way
it's supposed to work.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='814753' id='t-814753'>Support the idea of capping
